{"tid":1146409,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【安心牽連甚廣】配合重拍《法證IV》 李施嬅：生命中有時會做啱同錯","createTime":"2019-05-09T08:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T11:40:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c924e726285d240815e479ac5344db3167b398","tid":1146409,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"李施嬅今日到九龍塘一小學出席奧比斯護眼活動，提到無綫安排湯洛雯頂替黃心穎補拍《法證先鋒IV》，預計下月開工（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2vJrYGG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vJrYGG&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYXqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=b4f1b167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2vJrYGG</a> ），有份演出的施嬅說：「其實要拍幾多同拍幾耐，我自己都未知，不過我同心穎嘅戲份唔算多，最多係黃浩然，佢分別同心穎、Yumiko(鄭希怡)有感情線。」<br />\n施嬅稱已簽合約，稍後到外地工作，但確實時間未知，她會盡量協調及配合重拍《法證IV》，她說：「大家希望完成呢件事，因為辛苦咗五個幾月，好想見到成果。」<br />\n問她可有感到心穎一人犯錯，卻牽連甚廣？施嬅說：「始終冇人想發生呢啲事，生命中有時會做啱同錯，我哋應該以正能量去面對。」她表示事發後未有聯絡心穎，不過她跟馬國明有短訊聯絡：「我有text過佢，始終認識馬國明10幾年，我諗呢個時候，佢哋最需要就係空間。」<br />\n另一方面，施嬅在活動上與一班小朋友分享護眼心得，提到自己10多年前已接受激光矯視，她說：「近年發覺自己散光越嚟越嚴重，而且有乾眼症，可能因為拍嘢反光板光線太強，工作時間長加上以前護理得唔好，如果細心護理應該唔會有咁多問題。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190509/large/1557385718_2117.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190509%2Flarge%2F1557385718_2117.jpg&h=25909000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190509/59581256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190509%2F59581256&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYXqIiw1YZhwEtH0I4AgSOk0%3D&h=0ae168a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190509%2F59581256&h=472c7c92\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190509/59581256</a>"},{"pid":"506078c69b862b07e685f62e81556e6f3bb2ce36","tid":1146409,"uid":31024,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"佢同馬明先襯"},{"pid":"dcc1f3e5c8921c13742f87d38e4aec50a7bd9a8b","tid":1146409,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"另一方面，施嬅在活動上與一班小朋友分享<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">護眼心得</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"260b3d682009780992ed9c0e4d7845719cb06173","tid":1146409,"uid":29311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"506078c69b862b07e685f62e81556e6f3bb2ce36","tid":1146409,"uid":31024,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"佢同馬明先襯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"睇鐵馬尋橋嗰時覺得佢地好襯"},{"pid":"bef1f42b5d3aea24eabb03a8ae095db45da43d9d","tid":1146409,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:40:16.000Z","msg":"李校長辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}